      "content": "ugh this is so frustrating. i just want to know if taking 400mg every 2 or 3 hours is a normal thing to do to keep the level steady in my blood. i'm not trying to overdose or anything, i just dont want to be in agony again between doses. like, is a little more frequent dosing actually a common way to manage this?",
